name: ⁎̩͙ ⁑̩͙̩͙ ⁂̩̩͙͙ 　A Fairy Thanks　 ⁂̩̩͙͙ ⁑̩͙̩͙ ⁎̩͙
description:
Remember that day? When you thought you were dreaming, and maybe you were. Funny thing is, dreams are not antonyms of reality, press one finger against the other, your dreams are as real as that pressure on your skin.
This time you see a mirror, that comes like a caress on the back. A fairy's eyes dance in joy. She carries dandelions, fragrant of hope. She smiles not for herself, but because she's happy nature gave her two dandelions, so she can share one with you.
